er/20170603/large/1496468637_0588.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170603%2Flarge%2F1496468637_0588.jpg&h=e1f9d051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好勇敢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個marketing失蹤左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de23ba0b0088b0369426ae56fdc7ab7979ef03ca","tid":481053,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小藍單車係咪就係之前六四嗰陣喺北京成條長安大街排曬成列坦克車標志嘅單車嗰間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係<br />\n連登仔仲分析佢地有market sense 最睇好佢<br />\n點知極速收皮</blockquote><br />\n得罪方丈仲要踩到咁正理得你係阿里巴巴都要收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20170603/large/1496468637_0588.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170603%2Flarge%2F1496468637_0588.jpg&h=e1f9d051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好勇敢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個marketing失蹤左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe0f57ac9f5a6f2f09ba471c9ad784dde31c4de","tid":481053,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/11/1511461160_dp-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F11%2F1511461160_dp-1280w.jpg&h=8b297f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國共享單車公司曾經如雨後春筍般湧現，惟熱鬧過後不少已經倒閉，且大部分用戶都未能取回按金，中國傳媒「網易」根據公開資料推算，被拖欠的按金總數接近10億元(人民幣，下同)，輿論紛紛質問「押金去哪兒」之時，交通部表示正密切關注有關情況，並要求地方政府協助處理，深圳則計劃立例監管共享單車。<br />\n<br />\n網易指，已倒閉的共享單車公司，包括悟空單車、町町單車、小鳴單車、酷騎單車(圖)及小藍單車，除了悟空單車已全數退回按金外，酷騎、小藍及小鳴分別拖欠用戶約7億、2億及5,000萬元按金，町町則表示無法向一萬多名用戶退回按金，擬每人派一輛成本1,800元的單車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者：應好好建設信用體系<br />\n由於中國未有監管共享單車的法規，故地方政府相關部門都無法插手拖欠按金問題，只能建議消費者循司法途徑解決。新華社日前評論指，「押金難退折射出當下共享經濟盲目跟風的『創新之困』」，惟小藍單車有約100萬用戶透過信用體系免按金使用單車，避免了損失，故有學者認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">問題的核心在於「信用建設」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E6%B3%A1%E6%B2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4-%E5%82%B310%E5%84%84%E6%8C%89%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AA%E9%82%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6-105078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E5%2596%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%25B3%25A1%25E6%25B2%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25A0%25B4-%25E5%2582%25B310%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%258C%2589%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2582%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6-105078&d=xaBMCAPEdhMBgXjUKYuXTCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3eb66cab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E5%96%AE%E8%BB%8A%E6%B3%A1%E6%B2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%A0%B4-%E5%82%B310%E5%84%84%E6%8C%89%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AA%E9%82%84%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6-105078</a></blockquote><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">項莊舞劍<br />\n意在沛公</span></span></div></blockquote><br />\n芝麻信用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f801ca35a8901fdc37f9a7c52ea8a3605faaf19","tid":481053,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又幾似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb414d51f8aa269677bd3317730bd8799b2a066b","tid":481053,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"泡咩沫呀<img sr